div.div:
Refactor translation system to multi-chapter runs
Migrates from job-based to run-based architecture for book translation. Adds new services, parsers, exporters, and validators to support books with multiple chapters, translation runs, chapter translations, and export functionality. Updates API routes, tRPC routers, and UI pages to reflect the new structure. Removes obsolete job and chapter code, and updates database schema accordingly.

Add MVP translation SaaS core features and setup docs
Introduces core backend and frontend files for an AI-powered web novel translation SaaS, including DeepSeek API integration, TXT chapter parsing, translation job management, tRPC provider, and dashboard UI. Adds detailed README and SETUP documentation, Clerk authentication pages, SSE and upload API routes, and job processing logic. Refactors middleware location and updates job router for background translation processing.
Created new branch master in shinyPy/wn-tl-refactor
